@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hlvptq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.24 * tmp + 0.93) / (v1 + 0.47 * v2 + 0.49)) / (v0 + tmp))
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v2 = 0.17
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v1 + 0.35) - wp.sin(v2 + 0.75)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v1 / tmp))
    tmp = 0.21
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.49) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.53)))
    data[tid] = v0
